title: N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1647-8.4 - Schedule of replacement reserve transactions
content:
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 §§ 1647-8.4 - Schedule of replacement reserve transactions

State Regulations

This schedule shall be submitted, in an original and
duplicate, with the financial report submitted during the operating period for
the last quarter of the fiscal year, ending on March 31. The preparation of
this schedule is described on[FN*] section
1647-4.9. [FN*] So in original. Apparently should read
"in". Notes
N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9
§§
1647-8.4

State regulations are updated quarterly; we currently have two versions available. Below is a
comparison between our most recent version and the prior quarterly release. More comparison features will be added as we have more versions to compare. No prior version found.
